I have defined server end-point as:

@ServerEndpoint(value = "/ws/{mid}/{rid}/{uid}")

When using @PathParam with @OnMessage, values are null. Other annotations like @OnOpen and @OnClose print values specified in URL.

@OnMessage
public void onTextMessage(@PathParam("mid") Long mid, @PathParam("rid") Integer rid, @PathParam("uid") Long uid, Session session, String message, boolean pair) {
	log.debug("[TEXT]" + " : " + mid + " : " + rid + " : " + uid + message + " : " + session.getRequestURI());
}
